%% Diagram: TAO read and write paths
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant F as Follower\n(slave region)
    participant LB as Leader\n(slave region)
    participant LA as Leader\n(master region)
    participant DB as MySQL master

    Note over C,DB: Read — cache hit
    C->>F: assoc_range(...)
    F-->>C: cached prefix

    Note over C,DB: Read — cache miss
    C->>F: assoc_get(...)
    F->>LB: forward miss
    LB->>DB: SELECT (local slave DB)
    DB-->>LB: row(s)
    LB-->>F: data + version
    F-->>C: data

    Note over C,DB: Write (slave region)
    C->>F: assoc_add(...)
    F->>LB: forward write
    LB->>LA: cross-region forward
    LA->>DB: INSERT (write-through)
    DB-->>LA: ack
    LA-->>LB: changeset (+ inverse)
    LB-->>F: changeset (read-after-write)
    F-->>C: ack
    LA--)LB: async invalidate/refill
    LB--)F: async invalidate/refill
